Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就沒辦法了\N我會讓你痛快死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.31,0:02:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貳之秘劍 紅蓮腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.82,0:02:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄真實 你的人頭我要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.56,0:02:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牙突零式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.03,0:02:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大意？你在說什麼啊\N這叫做從容 知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.44,0:02:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二重極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.98,0:02:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 要下殺手或\N品味勝利的餘韻都還太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.69,0:02:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第五十九話\N運氣未盡 鬥志復甦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.38,0:03:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這喪家犬獨自跑來這兒 想做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喪家犬\N對 志志雄大人說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.29,0:03:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四乃森蒼紫\N你是輸給緋村的喪家犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.60,0:03:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一決雌雄的戰鬥\N沒你出場的份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.54,0:03:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是滾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.88,0:03:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫做方治是吧\N事實就是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.81,0:03:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不否定你喊我喪家犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.58,0:03:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 由於拔刀齊不避開\N與我這喪家犬的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.05,0:04:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而受了本來不該受的傷\N還連帶消耗體力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.46,0:04:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事 也是無法否定的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底想說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.47,0:04:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是你要禰捕那個傷是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.17,0:04:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算拔刀齊處於最佳狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他與志志雄大人的力量差距\N也是顯而易見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.71,0:04:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的作法\N是無法產生別的結果的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.18,0:04:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係的 方治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.82,0:04:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很久沒戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.15,0:04:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰是最強的人 這一點…\N我要讓他輸得心服口服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.93,0:04:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之 我打倒了緋村這幫人\N所以目前最強的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.24,0:04:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想不想打倒我\N讓御庭番眾的在天之靈們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獲得慰藉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.08,0:04:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同盟決裂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.69,0:05:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.62,0:05:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慢了 你的動作我全看清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.26,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 志志雄大人的猛攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.63,0:05:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓蒼紫那傢伙的兩把小太刀\N一點還擊餘地也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.97,0:05:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能忙著招架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.51,0:05:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不敢相信 竟然招架下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.44,0:05:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受了打倒宗次郎的\N拔刀齊的秘技天翔龍閃之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.38,0:05:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照理來說\N他應該連站著都很勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在居然還能\N與志志雄大人決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.86,0:05:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這男人的力量是從哪來的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.67,0:05:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四乃森蒼紫\N為什麼他能這樣打鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是因為他\N身為前御庭番眾的頭目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.04,0:05:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而執著於最強的稱號嗎\N還是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.96,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番式小太刀二刀流\N吳鉤十字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蠢蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.14,0:06:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打不倒拔刀齊的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.58,0:06:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為那種程度的絕招\N對我行得通？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑到背後了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.32,0:07:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 你把敵人逼到角落\N還使得敵人背向你了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.76,0:07:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站著發什麼呆\N這是最好的獲勝機會呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.89,0:07:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法攻擊嗎\N還是說你不想攻擊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.14,0:07:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那絕招是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.78,0:07:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番式小太刀二刀流\N回轉劍舞六連式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.78,0:07:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.79,0:07:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回轉劍舞六連式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.59,0:07:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是左右二選一\N瞬間六回轉的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.29,0:07:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如我所所料\N吃過天翔龍閃威力的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊力幾近於零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.97,0:08:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在你能辦的事\N打一開始就只有一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.47,0:08:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來拖延時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多悲慘的人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.18,0:08:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只一次\N接近修羅地獄的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.45,0:08:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在竭盡全力\N只能勉強來拖延時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.39,0:08:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是拔刀齊再也站不起來\N這不是一點意義也沒有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.49,0:08:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拖延時間？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四乃森蒼紫\N是為了拔刀齊而…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你終於瘋了 四乃森蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.17,0:08:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒看到拔刀齊那模樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.37,0:08:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人說的沒錯\N你再怎樣拖延時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.54,0:08:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊也是不可能復活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.54,0:08:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做的事\N只是執迷不悟的掙扎罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.49,0:08:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.93,0:09:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在生與死的修行中掙扎\N一定要活下去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.16,0:09:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我激發出與「捨身」截然不同的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.04,0:09:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學會最後的秘技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.57,0:09:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求生存的意志比什麼都強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.81,0:09:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是師父犧牲身體\N來讓我領悟到的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.99,0:09:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為斬人拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.73,0:09:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我犯下了無法挽回的滔天大罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.53,0:09:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以過去我心中決定自己\N是個隨時可以死的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.00,0:09:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現在不論發生什麼事\N我都絕不拋棄求生存的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.45,0:09:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還想打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.58,0:10:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼 為什麼要為\N不可能復活的拔刀齊而斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什麼支撐這男人站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.09,0:10:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四乃森蒼紫\N雖然你這個人格局小於緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.50,0:10:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在為人而動劍這點上面\N跟他屬於同類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.67,0:10:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟拔刀齊一樣\N在遇到我的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.71,0:10:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命運就走到盡頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.85,0:10:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道\N我與拔刀齊是不是同類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.89,0:10:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎樣都不認為他比你弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.23,0:10:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是喪家犬的遠吠呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的 志志雄大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.99,0:11:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村還沒恢復意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.72,0:11:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快給他斃命一擊 有那一擊\N國家就在我們手中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.44,0:11:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是起來戰鬥的時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.24,0:11:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在場的任何一個人\N命運都並沒有走到盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.15,0:11:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最終戰第二回合開始了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.43,0:11:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,樹葉對拔刀齊的劍氣產生反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.97,0:12:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊是不死怪物嗎\N不 我要冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.47,0:12:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他身受焰靈的燒傷\N與紅蓮腕的炸傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.24,0:12:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算沒死 也是元氣大傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.61,0:12:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算他有秘招天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.28,0:12:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是否能出招都大有疑問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.19,0:12:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是為何我會不寒而慄\N感到不安、恐懼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.92,0:12:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可小看…不可輕忽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.62,0:12:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村拔刀齊的存在\N已超越人智了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.06,0:12:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不認為志志雄大人會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.59,0:12:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.97,0:13:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還能站起來嘛\N害我為他白擔心一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.94,0:13:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我反而完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.68,0:13:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥之前他說不必插手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.51,0:13:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來最後還是只能依賴他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.79,0:13:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很爽快的劍氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.33,0:13:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 全力對抗我\N就是得超越一兩次界限才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.37,0:13:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 讓我這灼熱的血肉\N更灼熱、更痛快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 阻止這場戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.89,0:14:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經超出15分鐘了\N再打下去很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.76,0:14:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你忘了嗎？\N志志雄大人全身燒傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.77,0:14:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流汗會使他無法調節體溫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.57,0:14:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的身體被致命性的高熱所纏身呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.37,0:14:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是人類的體溫嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.28,0:14:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.65,0:14:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十年前全身燒傷後\N我的汗腺組織幾乎全死光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.55,0:14:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被致命性的高熱所纏身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.89,0:14:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以說  那是地獄業火的餘燼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.53,0:14:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餘燼…
