Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.33,0:16:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還早呢 還不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.00,0:16:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不讓你痛一回\N你就拿不出實力的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會再幫你一次
